thread.title: Eric Smith
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Eric Smith

author: Eric Smith
title: Eric Smith
text:
Ordered after lunch one day and received it after lunch the next day. Can't get better than that.
A Lot cheaper than Woolies.
Disappointment with the offer though on the back of the Wollies receipt. "additional 15% off" on COMPATIBLE CARTRIDGES ONLY.
What a lot of rubbish. I had one very common cartridge and one very unique cartridge. What do they mean "compatible?
